{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":2000,"text":"Please excuse me for sitting; I'm very old."},{"time":5000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":7000,"text":"Well, the topic I'm going to discuss"},{"time":9000,"text":"is one which is, in a certain sense, very peculiar"},{"time":12000,"text":"because it's very old."},{"time":14000,"text":"Roughness is part of human life"},{"time":17000,"text":"forever and forever,"},{"time":19000,"text":"and ancient authors have written about it."},{"time":22000,"text":"It was very much uncontrollable,"},{"time":24000,"text":"and in a certain sense,"},{"time":26000,"text":"it seemed to be the extreme of complexity,"},{"time":29000,"text":"just a mess, a mess and a mess."},{"time":31000,"text":"There are many different kinds of mess."},{"time":33000,"text":"Now, in fact,"},{"time":35000,"text":"by a complete fluke,"},{"time":37000,"text":"I got involved many years ago"},{"time":40000,"text":"in a study of this form of complexity,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and to my utter amazement,"},{"time":45000,"text":"I found traces --"},{"time":47000,"text":"very strong traces, I must say --"},{"time":49000,"text":"of order in that roughness."},{"time":52000,"text":"And so today, I would like to present to you"},{"time":54000,"text":"a few examples"},{"time":56000,"text":"of what this represents."},{"time":58000,"text":"I prefer the word roughness"},{"time":60000,"text":"to the word irregularity"},{"time":62000,"text":"because irregularity --"},{"time":64000,"text":"to someone who had Latin"},{"time":66000,"text":"in my long-past youth --"},{"time":68000,"text":"means the contrary of regularity."},{"time":70000,"text":"But it is not so."},{"time":72000,"text":"Regularity is the contrary of roughness"},{"time":75000,"text":"because the basic aspect of the world"},{"time":77000,"text":"is very rough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"So let me show you a few objects."},{"time":82000,"text":"Some of them are artificial."},{"time":84000,"text":"Others of them are very real, in a certain sense."},{"time":87000,"text":"Now this is the real. It's a cauliflower."},{"time":90000,"text":"Now why do I show a cauliflower,"},{"time":93000,"text":"a very ordinary and ancient vegetable?"},{"time":96000,"text":"Because old and ancient as it may be,"},{"time":99000,"text":"it's very complicated and it's very simple,"},{"time":102000,"text":"both at the same time."},{"time":104000,"text":"If you try to weigh it -- of course it's very easy to weigh it,"},{"time":107000,"text":"and when you eat it, the weight matters --"},{"time":110000,"text":"but suppose you try to"},{"time":113000,"text":"measure its surface."},{"time":115000,"text":"Well, it's very interesting."},{"time":117000,"text":"If you cut, with a sharp knife,"},{"time":120000,"text":"one of the florets of a cauliflower"},{"time":122000,"text":"and look at it separately,"},{"time":124000,"text":"you think of a whole cauliflower, but smaller."},{"time":127000,"text":"And then you cut again,"},{"time":129000,"text":"again, again, again, again, again, again, again, again,"},{"time":132000,"text":"and you still get small cauliflowers."},{"time":134000,"text":"So the experience of humanity"},{"time":136000,"text":"has always been that there are some shapes"},{"time":139000,"text":"which have this peculiar property,"},{"time":141000,"text":"that each part is like the whole,"},{"time":144000,"text":"but smaller."},{"time":146000,"text":"Now, what did humanity do with that?"},{"time":149000,"text":"Very, very little."},{"time":152000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"So what I did actually is to"},{"time":158000,"text":"study this problem,"},{"time":161000,"text":"and I found something quite surprising."},{"time":164000,"text":"That one can measure roughness"},{"time":167000,"text":"by a number, a number,"},{"time":170000,"text":"2.3, 1.2 and sometimes much more."},{"time":173000,"text":"One day, a friend of mine,"},{"time":175000,"text":"to bug me,"},{"time":177000,"text":"brought a picture and said,"},{"time":179000,"text":"\"What is the roughness of this curve?\""},{"time":181000,"text":"I said, \"Well, just short of 1.5.\""},{"time":184000,"text":"It was 1.48."},{"time":186000,"text":"Now, it didn't take me any time."},{"time":188000,"text":"I've been looking at these things for so long."},{"time":190000,"text":"So these numbers are the numbers"},{"time":192000,"text":"which denote the roughness of these surfaces."},{"time":195000,"text":"I hasten to say that these surfaces"},{"time":197000,"text":"are completely artificial."},{"time":199000,"text":"They were done on a computer,"},{"time":201000,"text":"and the only input is a number,"},{"time":203000,"text":"and that number is roughness."},{"time":206000,"text":"So on the left,"},{"time":208000,"text":"I took the roughness copied from many landscapes."},{"time":211000,"text":"To the right, I took a higher roughness."},{"time":214000,"text":"So the eye, after a while,"},{"time":216000,"text":"can distinguish these two very well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":219000,"text":"Humanity had to learn about measuring roughness."},{"time":221000,"text":"This is very rough, and this is sort of smooth, and this perfectly smooth."},{"time":224000,"text":"Very few things are very smooth."},{"time":228000,"text":"So then if you try to ask questions:"},{"time":231000,"text":"\"What's the surface of a cauliflower?\""},{"time":233000,"text":"Well, you measure and measure and measure."},{"time":236000,"text":"Each time you're closer, it gets bigger,"},{"time":239000,"text":"down to very, very small distances."},{"time":241000,"text":"What's the length of the coastline"},{"time":243000,"text":"of these lakes?"},{"time":245000,"text":"The closer you measure, the longer it is."},{"time":248000,"text":"The concept of length of coastline,"},{"time":250000,"text":"which seems to be so natural"},{"time":252000,"text":"because it's given in many cases,"},{"time":254000,"text":"is, in fact, complete fallacy; there's no such thing."},{"time":257000,"text":"You must do it differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"What good is that, to know these things?"},{"time":262000,"text":"Well, surprisingly enough,"},{"time":264000,"text":"it's good in many ways."},{"time":266000,"text":"To begin with, artificial landscapes,"},{"time":268000,"text":"which I invented sort of,"},{"time":270000,"text":"are used in cinema all the time."},{"time":273000,"text":"We see mountains in the distance."},{"time":275000,"text":"They may be mountains, but they may be just formulae, just cranked on."},{"time":278000,"text":"Now it's very easy to do."},{"time":280000,"text":"It used to be very time-consuming, but now it's nothing."},{"time":283000,"text":"Now look at that. That's a real lung."},{"time":286000,"text":"Now a lung is something very strange."},{"time":288000,"text":"If you take this thing,"},{"time":290000,"text":"you know very well it weighs very little."},{"time":293000,"text":"The volume of a lung is very small,"},{"time":295000,"text":"but what about the area of the lung?"},{"time":298000,"text":"Anatomists were arguing very much about that."},{"time":301000,"text":"Some say that a normal male's lung"},{"time":304000,"text":"has an area of the inside"},{"time":306000,"text":"of a basketball [court]."},{"time":308000,"text":"And the others say, no, five basketball [courts]."},{"time":312000,"text":"Enormous disagreements."},{"time":314000,"text":"Why so? Because, in fact, the area of the lung"},{"time":317000,"text":"is something very ill-defined."},{"time":320000,"text":"The bronchi branch, branch, branch"},{"time":323000,"text":"and they stop branching,"},{"time":326000,"text":"not because of any matter of principle,"},{"time":329000,"text":"but because of physical considerations:"},{"time":332000,"text":"the mucus, which is in the lung."},{"time":335000,"text":"So what happens is that in a way"},{"time":337000,"text":"you have a much bigger lung,"},{"time":339000,"text":"but it branches and branches"},{"time":341000,"text":"down to distances about the same for a whale, for a man"},{"time":344000,"text":"and for a little rodent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Now, what good is it to have that?"},{"time":350000,"text":"Well, surprisingly enough, amazingly enough,"},{"time":352000,"text":"the anatomists had a very poor idea"},{"time":355000,"text":"of the structure of the lung until very recently."},{"time":358000,"text":"And I think that my mathematics,"},{"time":360000,"text":"surprisingly enough,"},{"time":362000,"text":"has been of great help"},{"time":364000,"text":"to the surgeons"},{"time":366000,"text":"studying lung illnesses"},{"time":368000,"text":"and also kidney illnesses,"},{"time":370000,"text":"all these branching systems,"},{"time":372000,"text":"for which there was no geometry."},{"time":375000,"text":"So I found myself, in other words,"},{"time":377000,"text":"constructing a geometry,"},{"time":379000,"text":"a geometry of things which had no geometry."},{"time":382000,"text":"And a surprising aspect of it"},{"time":384000,"text":"is that very often, the rules of this geometry"},{"time":387000,"text":"are extremely short."},{"time":389000,"text":"You have formulas that long."},{"time":391000,"text":"And you crank it several times."},{"time":393000,"text":"Sometimes repeatedly: again, again, again,"},{"time":395000,"text":"the same repetition."},{"time":397000,"text":"And at the end, you get things like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"This cloud is completely,"},{"time":401000,"text":"100 percent artificial."},{"time":404000,"text":"Well, 99.9."},{"time":406000,"text":"And the only part which is natural"},{"time":408000,"text":"is a number, the roughness of the cloud,"},{"time":410000,"text":"which is taken from nature."},{"time":412000,"text":"Something so complicated like a cloud,"},{"time":414000,"text":"so unstable, so varying,"},{"time":416000,"text":"should have a simple rule behind it."},{"time":419000,"text":"Now this simple rule"},{"time":422000,"text":"is not an explanation of clouds."},{"time":425000,"text":"The seer of clouds had to"},{"time":427000,"text":"take account of it."},{"time":429000,"text":"I don't know how much advanced"},{"time":432000,"text":"these pictures are. They're old."},{"time":434000,"text":"I was very much involved in it,"},{"time":436000,"text":"but then turned my attention to other phenomena."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"Now, here is another thing"},{"time":441000,"text":"which is rather interesting."},{"time":444000,"text":"One of the shattering events"},{"time":446000,"text":"in the history of mathematics,"},{"time":448000,"text":"which is not appreciated by many people,"},{"time":451000,"text":"occurred about 130 years ago,"},{"time":453000,"text":"145 years ago."},{"time":455000,"text":"Mathematicians began to create"},{"time":457000,"text":"shapes that didn't exist."},{"time":459000,"text":"Mathematicians got into self-praise"},{"time":462000,"text":"to an extent which was absolutely amazing,"},{"time":464000,"text":"that man can invent things"},{"time":466000,"text":"that nature did not know."},{"time":468000,"text":"In particular, it could invent"},{"time":470000,"text":"things like a curve which fills the plane."},{"time":473000,"text":"A curve's a curve, a plane's a plane,"},{"time":475000,"text":"and the two won't mix."},{"time":477000,"text":"Well, they do mix."},{"time":479000,"text":"A man named Peano"},{"time":481000,"text":"did define such curves,"},{"time":483000,"text":"and it became an object of extraordinary interest."},{"time":486000,"text":"It was very important, but mostly interesting"},{"time":489000,"text":"because a kind of break,"},{"time":491000,"text":"a separation between"},{"time":493000,"text":"the mathematics coming from reality, on the one hand,"},{"time":496000,"text":"and new mathematics coming from pure man's mind."},{"time":499000,"text":"Well, I was very sorry to point out"},{"time":502000,"text":"that the pure man's mind"},{"time":504000,"text":"has, in fact,"},{"time":506000,"text":"seen at long last"},{"time":508000,"text":"what had been seen for a long time."},{"time":510000,"text":"And so here I introduce something,"},{"time":512000,"text":"the set of rivers of a plane-filling curve."},{"time":515000,"text":"And well,"},{"time":517000,"text":"it's a story unto itself."},{"time":519000,"text":"So it was in 1875 to 1925,"},{"time":522000,"text":"an extraordinary period"},{"time":524000,"text":"in which mathematics prepared itself to break out from the world."},{"time":527000,"text":"And the objects which were used"},{"time":529000,"text":"as examples, when I was"},{"time":531000,"text":"a child and a student, as examples"},{"time":533000,"text":"of the break between mathematics"},{"time":536000,"text":"and visible reality --"},{"time":538000,"text":"those objects,"},{"time":540000,"text":"I turned them completely around."},{"time":542000,"text":"I used them for describing"},{"time":544000,"text":"some of the aspects of the complexity of nature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"Well, a man named Hausdorff in 1919"},{"time":550000,"text":"introduced a number which was just a mathematical joke,"},{"time":553000,"text":"and I found that this number"},{"time":555000,"text":"was a good measurement of roughness."},{"time":557000,"text":"When I first told it to my friends in mathematics"},{"time":559000,"text":"they said, \"Don't be silly. It's just something [silly].\""},{"time":562000,"text":"Well actually, I was not silly."},{"time":565000,"text":"The great painter Hokusai knew it very well."},{"time":568000,"text":"The things on the ground are algae."},{"time":570000,"text":"He did not know the mathematics; it didn't yet exist."},{"time":573000,"text":"And he was Japanese who had no contact with the West."},{"time":576000,"text":"But painting for a long time had a fractal side."},{"time":579000,"text":"I could speak of that for a long time."},{"time":581000,"text":"The Eiffel Tower has a fractal aspect."},{"time":584000,"text":"I read the book that Mr. Eiffel wrote about his tower,"},{"time":587000,"text":"and indeed it was astonishing how much he understood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"This is a mess, mess, mess, Brownian loop."},{"time":593000,"text":"One day I decided --"},{"time":595000,"text":"halfway through my career,"},{"time":597000,"text":"I was held by so many things in my work --"},{"time":600000,"text":"I decided to test myself."},{"time":603000,"text":"Could I just look at something"},{"time":605000,"text":"which everybody had been looking at for a long time"},{"time":608000,"text":"and find something dramatically new?"},{"time":611000,"text":"Well, so I looked at these"},{"time":614000,"text":"things called Brownian motion -- just goes around."},{"time":617000,"text":"I played with it for a while,"},{"time":619000,"text":"and I made it return to the origin."},{"time":622000,"text":"Then I was telling my assistant,"},{"time":624000,"text":"\"I don't see anything. Can you paint it?\""},{"time":626000,"text":"So he painted it, which means"},{"time":628000,"text":"he put inside everything. He said:"},{"time":630000,"text":"\"Well, this thing came out ...\" And I said, \"Stop! Stop! Stop!"},{"time":633000,"text":"I see; it's an island.\""},{"time":636000,"text":"And amazing."},{"time":638000,"text":"So Brownian motion, which happens to have"},{"time":640000,"text":"a roughness number of two, goes around."},{"time":643000,"text":"I measured it, 1.33."},{"time":645000,"text":"Again, again, again."},{"time":647000,"text":"Long measurements, big Brownian motions,"},{"time":649000,"text":"1.33."},{"time":651000,"text":"Mathematical problem: how to prove it?"},{"time":654000,"text":"It took my friends 20 years."},{"time":657000,"text":"Three of them were having incomplete proofs."},{"time":660000,"text":"They got together, and together they had the proof."},{"time":664000,"text":"So they got the big [Fields] medal in mathematics,"},{"time":667000,"text":"one of the three medals that people have received"},{"time":669000,"text":"for proving things which I've seen"},{"time":672000,"text":"without being able to prove them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":675000,"text":"Now everybody asks me at one point or another,"},{"time":678000,"text":"\"How did it all start?"},{"time":680000,"text":"What got you in that strange business?\""},{"time":683000,"text":"What got you to be,"},{"time":685000,"text":"at the same time, a mechanical engineer,"},{"time":687000,"text":"a geographer"},{"time":689000,"text":"and a mathematician and so on, a physicist?"},{"time":691000,"text":"Well actually I started, oddly enough,"},{"time":694000,"text":"studying stock market prices."},{"time":696000,"text":"And so here"},{"time":698000,"text":"I had this theory,"},{"time":701000,"text":"and I wrote books about it --"},{"time":703000,"text":"financial prices increments."},{"time":705000,"text":"To the left you see data over a long period."},{"time":707000,"text":"To the right, on top,"},{"time":709000,"text":"you see a theory which is very, very fashionable."},{"time":712000,"text":"It was very easy, and you can write many books very fast about it."},{"time":715000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":717000,"text":"There are thousands of books on that."},{"time":720000,"text":"Now compare that with real price increments."},{"time":723000,"text":"Where are real price increments?"},{"time":725000,"text":"Well, these other lines"},{"time":727000,"text":"include some real price increments"},{"time":729000,"text":"and some forgery which I did."},{"time":731000,"text":"So the idea there was"},{"time":733000,"text":"that one must be able to -- how do you say? --"},{"time":735000,"text":"model price variation."},{"time":738000,"text":"And it went really well 50 years ago."},{"time":741000,"text":"For 50 years, people were sort of pooh-poohing me"},{"time":744000,"text":"because they could do it much, much easier."},{"time":746000,"text":"But I tell you, at this point, people listened to me."},{"time":749000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":751000,"text":"These two curves are averages:"},{"time":753000,"text":"Standard &amp; Poor, the blue one;"},{"time":755000,"text":"and the red one is Standard &amp; Poor's"},{"time":757000,"text":"from which the five biggest discontinuities"},{"time":760000,"text":"are taken out."},{"time":762000,"text":"Now discontinuities are a nuisance,"},{"time":764000,"text":"so in many studies of prices,"},{"time":767000,"text":"one puts them aside."},{"time":769000,"text":"\"Well, acts of God."},{"time":771000,"text":"And you have the little nonsense which is left."},{"time":774000,"text":"Acts of God.\" In this picture,"},{"time":777000,"text":"five acts of God are as important as everything else."},{"time":780000,"text":"In other words,"},{"time":782000,"text":"it is not acts of God that we should put aside."},{"time":784000,"text":"That is the meat, the problem."},{"time":787000,"text":"If you master these, you master price,"},{"time":790000,"text":"and if you don't master these, you can master"},{"time":792000,"text":"the little noise as well as you can,"},{"time":794000,"text":"but it's not important."},{"time":796000,"text":"Well, here are the curves for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":798000,"text":"Now, I get to the final thing, which is the set"},{"time":800000,"text":"of which my name is attached."},{"time":802000,"text":"In a way, it's the story of my life."},{"time":804000,"text":"My adolescence was spent"},{"time":806000,"text":"during the German occupation of France."},{"time":808000,"text":"Since I thought that I might"},{"time":811000,"text":"vanish within a day or a week,"},{"time":814000,"text":"I had very big dreams."},{"time":817000,"text":"And after the war,"},{"time":819000,"text":"I saw an uncle again."},{"time":821000,"text":"My uncle was a very prominent mathematician, and he told me,"},{"time":823000,"text":"\"Look, there's a problem"},{"time":825000,"text":"which I could not solve 25 years ago,"},{"time":827000,"text":"and which nobody can solve."},{"time":829000,"text":"This is a construction of a man named [Gaston] Julia"},{"time":831000,"text":"and [Pierre] Fatou."},{"time":833000,"text":"If you could"},{"time":835000,"text":"find something new, anything,"},{"time":837000,"text":"you will get your career made.\""},{"time":839000,"text":"Very simple."},{"time":841000,"text":"So I looked,"},{"time":843000,"text":"and like the thousands of people that had tried before,"},{"time":845000,"text":"I found nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"But then the computer came,"},{"time":850000,"text":"and I decided to apply the computer,"},{"time":852000,"text":"not to new problems in mathematics --"},{"time":855000,"text":"like this wiggle wiggle, that's a new problem --"},{"time":857000,"text":"but to old problems."},{"time":859000,"text":"And I went from what's called"},{"time":861000,"text":"real numbers, which are points on a line,"},{"time":863000,"text":"to imaginary, complex numbers,"},{"time":865000,"text":"which are points on a plane,"},{"time":867000,"text":"which is what one should do there,"},{"time":869000,"text":"and this shape came out."},{"time":871000,"text":"This shape is of an extraordinary complication."},{"time":874000,"text":"The equation is hidden there,"},{"time":876000,"text":"z goes into z squared, plus c."},{"time":879000,"text":"It's so simple, so dry."},{"time":881000,"text":"It's so uninteresting."},{"time":883000,"text":"Now you turn the crank once, twice:"},{"time":886000,"text":"twice,"},{"time":889000,"text":"marvels come out."},{"time":891000,"text":"I mean this comes out."},{"time":893000,"text":"I don't want to explain these things."},{"time":895000,"text":"This comes out. This comes out."},{"time":897000,"text":"Shapes which are of such complication,"},{"time":899000,"text":"such harmony and such beauty."},{"time":902000,"text":"This comes out"},{"time":904000,"text":"repeatedly, again, again, again."},{"time":906000,"text":"And that was one of my major discoveries,"},{"time":908000,"text":"to find that these islands were the same"},{"time":910000,"text":"as the whole big thing, more or less."},{"time":912000,"text":"And then you get these"},{"time":914000,"text":"extraordinary baroque decorations all over the place."},{"time":917000,"text":"All that from this little formula,"},{"time":920000,"text":"which has whatever, five symbols in it."},{"time":923000,"text":"And then this one."},{"time":925000,"text":"The color was added for two reasons."},{"time":927000,"text":"First of all, because these shapes"},{"time":929000,"text":"are so complicated"},{"time":932000,"text":"that one couldn't make any sense of the numbers."},{"time":935000,"text":"And if you plot them, you must choose some system."},{"time":938000,"text":"And so my principle has been"},{"time":940000,"text":"to always present the shapes"},{"time":943000,"text":"with different colorings"},{"time":945000,"text":"because some colorings emphasize that,"},{"time":947000,"text":"and others it is that or that."},{"time":949000,"text":"It's so complicated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":951000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":953000,"text":"In 1990, I was in Cambridge, U.K."},{"time":955000,"text":"to receive a prize from the university,"},{"time":958000,"text":"and three days later,"},{"time":960000,"text":"a pilot was flying over the landscape and found this thing."},{"time":963000,"text":"So where did this come from?"},{"time":965000,"text":"Obviously, from extraterrestrials."},{"time":967000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":970000,"text":"Well, so the newspaper in Cambridge"},{"time":972000,"text":"published an article about that \"discovery\""},{"time":974000,"text":"and received the next day"},{"time":976000,"text":"5,000 letters from people saying,"},{"time":978000,"text":"\"But that's simply a Mandelbrot set very big.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":982000,"text":"Well, let me finish."},{"time":984000,"text":"This shape here just came"},{"time":986000,"text":"out of an exercise in pure mathematics."},{"time":988000,"text":"Bottomless wonders spring from simple rules,"},{"time":991000,"text":"which are repeated without end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":994000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}